    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "🤖 AI Customer Support Agent Workflow\n\nReceives support tickets via Webhook in real time, \nsearches a knowledge base for solutions, uses AI to \ngenerate replies and escalates to a human if unsolved.\n\nNodes:\n**Step 1**\n▶ Webhook — Receives customer support tickets instantly\n\n**Step 2**\n📊 Google Sheets — Reads knowledge base solutions\n\n**Step 3**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript — Matches issue to knowledge base\n\n**Step 4**\n🤖 OpenAI — Generates AI powered support reply\n\n**Step 5**\n🔀 IF — Checks if AI resolved the issue\n\n**Step 6**\n✅ TRUE: Code in JavaScript1 — Cleans resolved ticket data\n\n**Step 7**\n📧 TRUE: Gmail — Sends resolution draft to customer\n\n**Step 8**\n⚙️ TRUE: Code in JavaScript2 — Prepares logging data\n\n**Step 9**\n📊 TRUE: Google Sheets1 — Logs resolved ticket\n\n**Step 10**\n❌ FALSE: Gmail1 — Escalates to human agent",
        "height": 688,
        "width": 576
      },
